test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (3 == 3 and 0 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7b516f85ab40>([-61])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7b516f85ab40> = [[1, -61, 1, -61], [-61], [1, -61, 1, -61], [-61], [1, -61, 1, -61], [-61]].count
 +  and   0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7b516f85ab40>([1, -61])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7b516f85ab40> = [[1, -61, 1, -61], [-61], [1, -61, 1, -61], [-61], [1, -61, 1, -61], [-61]].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -226981 == -61
 +  where -226981 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -61, -1, -1, -61, -1, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
